{"type":"message","id":"f6fbb401","parentId":"e5d51935","timestamp":"2026-03-19T20:44:15.374Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 04:44 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 请搜索以下道简网络相关行业的最新动态：\n\n1. 企业数字化转型最新政策/趋势\n2. 智能安防行业动态\n3. 网络系统集成行业动态\n4. IT运维服务行业趋势\n\n请搜索2026年3月的最新信息，整理3-5条关键信息，以简洁的笔记格式输出。"}],"timestamp":1773953055370}}
{"type":"message","id":"c2f53d7f","parentId":"f6fbb401","timestamp":"2026-03-19T20:44:23.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户需要我搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态，包括：\n1. 企业数字化转型最新政策/趋势\n2. 智能安防行业动态\n3. 网络系统集成行业动态\n4. IT运维服务行业趋势\n\n需要搜索2026年3月的最新信息，整理3-5条关键信息，以简洁的笔记格式输出。\n\n我需要使用web-search skill来搜索这些信息。让我先读取这个skill。","thinkingSignature":"03f2c4ccea63da9fd6ca1d94fbd90a689ca9fedfe4e0b0f11edf199042aa6de2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mszc8waplyk1_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":117,"output":128,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":30745,"totalTokens":30990,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0001536,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0036894,"total":0.0038780999999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773953055372}}
{"type":"message","id":"cad75f01","parentId":"c2f53d7f","timestamp":"2026-03-19T20:44:23.446Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_mszc8waplyk1_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773953063444}}
{"type":"message","id":"1261652e","parentId":"cad75f01","timestamp":"2026-03-19T20:44:35.191Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我现在了解了如何使用web-search skill。我需要搜索4个方面的信息：\n1. 企业数字化转型最新政策/趋势 2026年3月\n2. 智能安防行业动态 2026年3月\n3. 网络系统集成行业动态 2026年3月\n4. IT运维服务行业趋势 2026年3月\n\n让我分别进行搜索。我可以并行执行多个搜索。","thinkingSignature":"0b3363e09f0d253559143a95ef9e72da4d02fa4e271d310e771711fea9196dfc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u1dweas7cia0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型最新政策 2026年3月\"","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u1dweas7cia0_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026年3月\"","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u1dweas7cia0_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成行业趋势 2026年3月\"","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u1dweas7cia0_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务行业发展趋势 2026年3月\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":891,"output":286,"cacheRead":30614,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31791,"cost":{"input":0.0002673,"output":0.0003432,"cacheRead":0.0009184199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0015289199999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773953063446}}
